# Content Portage cannot ship. Engines come from Portage only — its own
# Manifest verification already covers them.
#
# Format, one entry per line:
#
#   sha256 | dest relative to $HOME | mirror URLs, primary first
#
# The hash is the truth: a file that does not match it is discarded, and
# the next mirror is tried. Fetched by assets.sh, called from install.sh.

