# Brutal Doom — NOT PINNED YET, needs a hash from you.
#
# The author's canonical release is ModDB, which serves its downloads from
# behind a bot wall: it cannot be fetched non-interactively, so the hash
# could not be verified from here. There is no SgtMarkIV/BrutalDoom GitHub
# repo to fall back on. Pinning a hash copied from memory or from a random
# third-party mirror would be worse than leaving this out: hash-as-truth
# means a wrong hash rejects the *right* file forever, and an unofficial
# mirror pinned by hash is a supply chain you did not choose.
#
# To pin it, download the pk3 from ModDB by hand, then:
#     sha256sum brutalv22.pk3
# and uncomment this line with that hash filled in:
#
# <sha256> | .local/share/games/doom/brutalv22.pk3 | <url>
